29:15.113 --> 29:21.202
She's been listening closely to the story that God's telling for five months now.

29:22.498 --> 29:34.002
In solitude, Elizabeth found herself in the unfolding story of God's redemption, and she began to see beyond just the surface of things to the way that God is conspiring to renew the whole world.

29:34.370 --> 29:41.918
and the ordinary people and circumstances of her life, even right in the midst of her deepest pain and most long-lasting grief.

29:42.319 --> 29:54.172
In the quiet, God is slowly peeling Elizabeth's eyes open to behold her tiny personal story in light of his massive renewal story.

29:54.833 --> 30:03.282
In the quiet as she listened to God and chewed on his promises, Elizabeth began to wonder, could it really be

30:05.442 --> 30:12.411
that I'm in line with Sarah and Rebecca and Rachel and Hannah.

30:13.652 --> 30:18.759
