30:18.819 --> 30:29.092
Could it really be that I matter so much to God that he would write me into a cast member role in his redemption?

30:32.116 --> 30:33.778
And when she dares to believe,

30:34.402 --> 30:40.592
that she is as important to God as God is showing her that she is.

30:41.573 --> 30:46.100
All of a sudden, she is able to uncover and call the same thing out of others.

30:46.942 --> 30:52.470
Who am I that the mother of my Lord would come to me?

30:53.852 --> 31:02.706
Do you see when Elizabeth begins to believe in her own identity as God is naming it, she begins to draw the same out of the other people who come to knock on her door?

31:04.450 --> 31:06.153
And finally, John.

31:06.193 --> 31:14.125
In the teaching test we read to begin, when their child or their promised child is born, Zechariah's silence is finally broken.

31:14.205 --> 31:17.890
