33:20.530 --> 33:21.712
Eremos.

33:23.854 --> 33:26.418
Jesus often withdrew into seclusion.

33:26.978 --> 33:29.061
into solitude, into the wilderness.

33:30.743 --> 33:45.661
Jesus chose Advent's invitation again and again and again, zig, while the world around you is zagging, when the noise gets loud as retreat into the quiet, when the world is busiest, but come still and listen, that's where God has found, that's where we are formed.

