And if Jesus needed the practice of silence and solitude, how much more do we?

34:41.009 --> 34:52.466
Yeah, but I've got a toddler and an infant at home right now and you don't understand if Jesus needed the practice of silence and solitude, how much more do we?

34:53.922 --> 34:57.026
Sure, but I work in marketing and retail, and it's December.

