36:57.480 --> 37:07.191
There are endless varieties of ways that you and I can conspire to avoid peace in reality because we are seeking peace in abstraction.

37:07.712 --> 37:13.138
The only way to know real peace is by subtraction.

37:14.018 --> 37:29.185
It is to allow silence to strip you of every other input to expose every disordered attachment, control mechanism and compulsion, leaving you with nothing but the reality of your bare self in God's loving presence.

37:29.205 --> 37:36.818
Peace cannot be circumstantial because there is no life script that protects us from pain.

