And if you are the image of the invisible God, first born over all of creation, victor over sin, suffering, death, and the grave, perfect relationship with God, self, and others, then one of your disciples will betray you and be unable to bear the guilt of seeing them real selves, and they will take their life while you're reclaiming your own,

39:31.728 --> 39:35.932
