True peace is forged when I get slow and quiet enough to face my darkness and allow God's real presence to meet my real pain, his warmth, my winter.

40:02.306 --> 40:09.214
Psychological consensus affirms that growth occurs when we're pushed about 10% beyond our current capacity.

