46:52.546 --> 47:15.602
slip away into solitude, hide yourself away like Jesus this Advent season and you will face the pain and grief that you keep buried, shoveling busyness and noise and distraction over all of it until you see finally what you've tried not to face and you will meet the unconditional love of God.

47:16.706 --> 47:23.653
right in the midst of your unique mess and your unique pain saying, I love you.

47:23.673 --> 47:25.815
I love you.

